Annotation Interface MBeanNotifications

@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: MBeanNotifications.java 995 2022-01-23 01:09:35Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.0.1") @Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) @Inherited public @interface MBeanNotifications
This annotation will be used to declare more than one MBean notification for a class or a method.
